qMsg.qv: ='There are no billable runs found within the current selection state.'

qStringExpression.qExpr:
=If($(vCheckForThirdPartyRunsLicense) AND [Runs Billable CMTD]>0,
	'Forecasting a quota usage change by end-of-month from ' & Round([Runs Billable CMTD % Quota]*100,.1) & '% to ' & Round(($(vForecastRunBillableMax) / Only({<AutomationQuotaType={'3rdPartyAutomationRuns'}>} AutomationQuota)) * 100,.1) & '% of ' & Num(Only({<AutomationQuotaType={'3rdPartyAutomationRuns'}>} AutomationQuota),'#,##0'),
    ''
)

qMsg.qv: ='There are no standard runs found within the current selection state.'

qStringExpression.qExpr:
=If($(vCheckForStandardRunsLicense) AND [Runs Standard CMTD]>0,
	'Forecasting a quota usage change by end-of-month from ' & Round([Runs Standard CMTD % Quota]*100,.1) & '% to ' & Round(($(vForecastRunMax) / Only({<AutomationQuotaType={'standardAutomationRuns'}>} AutomationQuota)) * 100,.1) & '% of ' & Num(Only({<AutomationQuotaType={'standardAutomationRuns'}>} AutomationQuota),'#,##0'),
    ''
)
